awp_protection_alpha by vNy

Thank you for downloading my map. It's my first map. To install it,
just copy the .bsp file into your cstrike/maps folder. If you  want 
to use it in your project, credit me please.

I'm working on the following things for the final version:

- Bots
- Ambient light
- Make it more "normal", not like a arena (Add objects)
- Change Skybox
- Some structure changes

You have ideas or critics?
Write it here: https://login.4players.de/guestbook.php/de/cs/1963436/
or here:       http://www.fpsbanana.com/members/1049111

Thank you guys!
Your vNy
